{"type": "article", "id": 37286, "title": "仔细看这青花瓷，上面有外星人｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-26T03:54:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30154, "name": "Form us with love"}, {"id": 37173, "name": "Calamityware"}, {"id": 37174, "name": "Mary’s"}, {"id": 37175, "name": "BramCreates"}, {"id": 37176, "name": "WIFF"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 37177, "name": "poli-Studio"}, {"id": 37178, "name": "Don Moyer"}, {"id": 37179, "name": "Sabeene Karnik"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 170, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170126093131GUpyCLx5YAQsdHS6.png", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Calamityware by Don Moyer</h3><p>谁说瓷器上的纹饰就一定得走精致却毫无新意的古典路线？2011 年，当美国平面设计师 Don Moyer 为一张被视作传家宝的瓷盘作画时，他突发奇想，决定让这件古董变得更有趣一些。当你仔细观察这套名为 <a href=\"http://calamityware.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Calamityware</a> 的蓝白瓷盘时，会意外地发现诸如 UFO、疑似外星生物以及巨型机器人的乱入，和看上去规规矩矩的风景形成了一种有趣的反差。这四款瓷盘曾在 2014 年做过一次众筹，Moyer 最近在第一版的基础上又加入了一些新元素作为惊喜。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/159974695/calamityware-series-1-revisited\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 42 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093256EOPeUqpoXk3J52li.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093256d1RzyfYgJB3iNjeK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093256LEWbIh7q4tOkZgM3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093256xLVwcfSpk0Es15nZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093259HSeIswTCKOaYEn10.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Maskal by poli-Studio</h3><p>长时间佩戴口罩后，是不是会觉得耳朵后面有点疼？为了减少这种疼痛，日本机械设计公司 poli-Studio 的创始人野崎靖开发了这款采用 3D 打印技术的口罩架 Maskal。它由柔软的硅胶制成，号称可以适应不同的脸型。从外观上来看，你可以把 Maskal 理解为变形的眼镜架，其实相当于增大了施力面：将其穿过普通的口罩后，只要把两端经耳垂下方搭住耳后即可。这种像戴眼镜一样的方式也让摘口罩和收口罩变得容易了一些，只要轻轻一拨，挂在桌沿就行了。除此之外，架子中央贴住鼻子的部分还撑出了额外的呼吸空间，不会让人觉得呼吸困难。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/maskal/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 3000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093219AfjeLsTS72JtuqWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093217CQmibhws90f2cvSU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093217t1DMSlYPv9RokOBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093218vVYjdr7PNq1ipuF4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093217HF9hcP4Y3jJ516lu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093219BTbEZU2aDl1cHFXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kungsbacka by Form Us With Love</h3><p>我们曾在去年报道过宜家越来越重视<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28394.html\">环保材料的使用</a>，最近瑞典设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.formuswithlove.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Form Us With Love</a> 就公布了为宜家设计的模块化厨房柜 Kungsbacka。你或许会觉得它们看上去并没有什么特别，但这些柜子其实都是百分之百的环保产品，所用到的仅仅是二次利用的工业木料以及被加工为涂层的塑料瓶。设计师们希望以此挑战人们对环保材料的偏见：只要利用得当，它们也可以重生为实用而且价格也不昂贵的产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093315hK0lk2Y9md6cb7wy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701260933154ZB7kdQpr1FeLqw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093315b04DTmCXZWE8kHwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.162860\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701260933153YzdbI72tWsUQrEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093315QTNm1t8sc24XW3kn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093316H76yaGcoW3MtTSn5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paper typography by Sabeene Karnik</h3><p>同样是折纸，印度孟买的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sabeenu\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sabeene Karnik</a> 擅长将它们排版成一个个漂亮的图案或是字母。这些精致的作品相当依赖大小和结构的精确度，每一件都是 Karnik 在数次测量和微调后完成的。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.sabeenakarnik.bigcartel.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到她的部分作品，售价从 50 美元起。如果你对她的作品感兴趣的话，可以关注她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sabeenu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093448jM7rT9q4uNFBSQYo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093448mGgq7nBX6Ouz43Di.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.102000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701260934490WbD3iNOUuYf4dJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093448pFTbAWMkhtI8wOPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093449Eg0HdqyNAstJTbDu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093448TIiEQenBsz2JjF8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.757000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tsuwamono by Mary’s</h3><p>说起情人节，你可能多少也听说过日本商家每年为此做出的各类限定版巧克力。巧克力品牌 Mary’s 今年就推出了一套以战国时代的知名武将为主题的巧克力系列 Tsuwamono。它一共分为四种礼盒，印有武将头盔的红蓝黑三款分别代表了真田信繁、伊达政宗和织田信长。巧克力的造型和口味也与人物息息相关，比如织田“熱き者”巧克力就是以他的佩刀为灵感设计的。第四款礼盒被称为“疾風の者”，代表了来无影去无踪的忍者们，里面装着的是手里剑造型的巧克力。这是它的<a href=\"http://maryshop.jp/shop/e/evttuwamo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 648 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093332glEy2xDHQh5fImcu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701724\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093332j9XLrcJDInlwPHva.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713793\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093332RIicENqwAUKBQGDr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777586\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093332cJVbda6tsmMSUTK3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.541379\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>WIFF by BramCreates</h3><p>厌倦了越来越多的蜡烛和香薰采用相似的原料，英国曼彻斯特的 Claire 和 Graeme Winchester 为此创立了一个名为 <a href=\"http://wiff.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WIFF</a> 的品牌，充满创意的香型组合是它的一大特色。为了强调这种差异，创意机构 <a href=\"http://bramcreates.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BramCreates</a> 将每一种香型的特点通过活泼的配色和相应的要素，以类似拼图的印象画的形式呈现在包装上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348Amks4KRzeraUFlwZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348Sy4Dc1iYjF6JOqbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348zvnDbaNBqsFKWmX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348EuZv8rYXIqkytewF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348y0VtKnXewUjI8igM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126093348U78DiJwfGjtcOPvb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}